00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:15,560
Think about some of the words that we've just discussed and we'll be back in a moment.
想想我们刚刚讨论过的一些单词，我们一会儿就回来。

249
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:18,400
Last will and testament of Luke Thompson.
卢克·汤普森的最终遗嘱。

